Author: donout_disturb
Text: You're not alone.  Either I restrict or I binge, that's how I "cope" with my problems and it sucks because it doesn't even help.  What a shitty coping mechanism. :')

Author: slug_93
Text: Nope, very common! EDs are common a (maladaptive) distress tolerance technique; the “distress” is often nothing to do with food at all.
